snippet: Factory activity in Europe and Asia cooled in August after a strong July, as new orders dwindled in the face of escalating tensions in Ukraine and a patchy recovery in China, purchasing managers indexes showed....

headline.print_headline: Factory Activity in Europe, Asia Cools; Demand Lull a Concern
headline.main: Factory Activity in Europe, Asia Cools; Demand Lull a Concern

lead_paragraph: Factory activity in Europe and Asia cooled in August after a strong July, as new orders dwindled in the face of escalating tensions in Ukraine and a patchy recovery in China, purchasing managers indexes showed.
